-- Berkshire Hills sees earnings below estimates
-- 
-- Mon Jul 30, 2007 10:58am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/07/30/us-berkshirehills-outlook-idUSWNAS855620070730

 

 (Reuters) - Bank holding company Berkshire Hills Bancorp Inc. BHLB.O forecast third-quarter earnings below analysts' estimates. 

 In a conference call, the company said it expects earnings of about 50 cents a share for the third quarter. Analysts on average expect the company to earn 54 cents a share, before items, according to Reuters Estimates. Shares of the company were down almost 2 percent at $27.43 in morning trade on the Nasdaq. (Reporting by Avishek Mishra in Bangalore)